snippet.title: Charles Haunted Mansion Official Steam Trailer - A 2D Survival Horror
snippet.description:
#horrorgaming #steamgame #pcgame 
Check it out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2569680/Charles_Haunted_Mansion/

Charles Haunted Mansion is a 2D Top-Down Survival Horror game based on the story of a mansion, haunted by the vengeful spirit of a woman who was murdered inside the mansion decades ago.
